desc_long								关于这款游戏							Sumico is Match3 with numbers. “One of the best puzzle games in years!” The press adores Sumico. And so will you. Sumico is a must-have title for fans of puzzle games! Easy to pick up, fun to play, challenging if you want it to be. Smooth graphics, nice music and most importantly: an incredibly smart puzzle. But, don’t take our word for it: many, many professional reviewers awarded Sumico a 9 out of 10. Among them are publications like Family Friendly Gaming, App4Smart, Nintendolife and Brashgames. Sumico Deluxe Edition comes with an incredible amount of gameplay. A huge campaign containing 84 handmade levels will entertain you for hours on end. For a different kind of challenge, try the Endless Mode which is, indeed, endless fun! Sumico contains an easier mode for kids and an educational mode which adheres to official mathematical rules.Match 3 with numbers	Easy to pick up, fun to play	Educational mode	84 levels + Endless Mode	Great reviews by the press!						
